RŻENIE KONI W TLE

00:40:09.199 --> 00:40:16.679 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Wasz wuj, Odolan, z Wieletami
najechał waszego brata!

00:40:17.400 --> 00:40:20.599 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Na czele ogromny rycerz

00:40:22.880 --> 00:40:24.280 line:85% position:50% size:80%
z żelaza!

00:40:24.800 --> 00:40:26.159 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Wichman!

00:40:26.487 --> 00:40:30.909 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
